				]
			},
			{
				"name": "Soviet Bloc",
				"additionalRules": [
					"Harmonic Resonance - At the start of every turn, roll a D6 for each enemy unit on the table that does not have the Fearless special rule. On a 5+, that unit immediately receives a Pin Marker; Konflikt '47 Army List - Soviet Bloc: Pg. 2",
					"Za Stalina - Whenever an Infantry or Artillery unit fails a Morale Check and would be destroyed, reroll it and apply the second result instead. If a test is passed in this way, that unit is immediately up-rated to the next Quality Level for the rest of the game. If it was a Veteran unit, it gains +1 Morale Value instead; Konflikt '47 Army List - Soviet Bloc: Pg. 2",
					"Heroes of the Soviet Bloc - At the start of the game, before deployment, one non-Hero, non-Rift Infantry Unit may be designated 'Heroes of the Soviet Bloc'. The chosen unit immediately gains a point of Guts. Friendly units within 6in gain Fanatics; Konflikt '47 Army List - Soviet Bloc: Pg. 2",
